dcterms:description: The CelebA-HQ dataset is a high-quality face dataset derived from CelebA, comprising 30,000 images of 1024 × 1024 resolution faces featuring approximately 6,000 unique identities. It was curated by extracting faces from the original dataset based on facial landmarks and enhancing image quality using a GAN-trained super-resolution model.
dcterms:title: CelebA-HQ

dcterms:description: B3FD is a dataset that merges two large web-based datasets, focusing on cleaning web-scraped facial datasets by automatically removing erroneous samples to enhance usability. It contains 375,592 images with 53,759 unique subjects, with age labels ranging from 0 to 100.
dcterms:title: B3FD
